  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is to be investigated if a correlation exist between the development of the HbA1c value
      and the complication rate is following a stroke.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The immediate objective of the study is to find out if a correlation between blood sugar
      control in diabetics and the incidence of complications after a stroke exists.

      The study has a high practical importance because any consequences in the treatment of
      diabetes mellitus can be implemented without affecting costs.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
